    <div class="section-label">/ Thoughts</div>
    <h2>Writing.<br>Occasionally.</h2>

    <div class="thoughts-list">

      <!-- Thought entries — replace with real posts -->
      <a href="#" class="thought-item">
        <div class="thought-date">Mar 2025</div>
        <div>
          <div class="thought-title">On the permanence of impermanence</div>
          <div class="thought-preview">Why physical media matters in a world of infinite streaming. A record doesn't disappear when a service shuts down.</div>
        </div>
